$ and the bound state of $\\bar{D}^* \\Sigma_c^*$ with a mass of\nabout 4520 MeV, do not decay into $\\eta_c N$. Therefore, the $\\eta_c N$ channel\nshould be studied in future to provide further insights into the nature of\nthese states, especially that of the $P_c(4440)$ and $P_c(4457)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Jul 2020 16:17:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Jul 2020 14:31:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-23"}
